<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>About | Weather App</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/image/Weather.webp">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main-content">
        {{>header}}

        <div class="about-container">
            <img class="portrait" src="/image/simar.png" alt="Simar Singh Narang" />
            <h2>About the Weather App</h2>
            <p>
                This weather application provides real-time weather updates, including temperature, humidity,
                air quality, wind speed, and more. Stay prepared for any weather conditions with accurate forecasts.
            </p>

            <h3>Features:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Live temperature and weather conditions</li>
                <li>Sunrise and sunset timings</li>
                <li>Air Quality Index for health awareness</li>
                <li>Wind speed and direction details</li>
                <li>Rain and cloud coverage predictions</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Developer:</h3>
            <p><strong>{{name}}</strong></p>
            <p>Passionate about creating useful and interactive web applications.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    {{>footer}}
</body>

</html>